{"tid":2301140,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]GUNDAM BATTLE OPERATION 2 [92] 從此再沒地宇機之分","createTime":"2020-11-26T05:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T12:15:53.000Z","uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"193e1fa6e8779488ed8ba82ebbfc16393a6a2006","tid":2301140,"uid":7232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T05:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dXnLhmM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdXnLhmM.jpg&h=53f39183&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日文官網: <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=391cb995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp</a><br />\n中文官網 : <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp%2Fhk%2F&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=6c8ffdcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/</a><br />\n遊戲Wiki: <a href=\"https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fbattle-operation2&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=7a381e7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2</a><br />\nGBO2 機體表<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X2Hi5dLqjym5hvqX0q4NeNr_B6Eqi4Yz9Vvoapzae3s/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X2Hi5dLqjym5hvqX0q4NeNr_B6Eqi4Yz9Vvoapzae3s%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=6b84e77f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X2Hi5dLqjym5hvqX0q4NeNr_B6Eqi4Yz9Vvoapzae3s/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n新手注意<br />\n溫馨提示:咩都唔識就搵𡃁妹玩下訓練先<br />\n順手拎部200cost神器訓練吉<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKEKMn0X1MHk&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=68035caf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk</a><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\nFAQ<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解我成日斷線<br />\nA. 為己為人, 自殺對戰請用Lan 線<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ. 今集有無EN限制?係咪好似上集兩個鐘先回1粒EN?<br />\nA. 今集廢除咗EN, 玩真人體力制, 燃燒自己嘅小宇宙啦<br />\n<br />\nQ. 有無分Server? 用港定日psn 好?<br />\nA. 今集係國際Server, 港日psn 都係一齊玩, 但之前GBON轉Server 前科, 所以用日psn應該會安全啲<br />\n<br />\nQ. 可唔可以同朋友一齊開房玩<br />\nA. Ranking 同Quick請用正方入房之後邀朋友, 自訂直接入房之後邀朋友<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣用支援炮擊<br />\nA. 佔點之後會見到有個數字倒數, 當倒數到0之後就可以落機call 炮擊, 威力極大如善用可以一擊逆轉戰況<br />\n<br />\nQ. 機/武/Parts 點樣升lv?<br />\nA. 用DP直接買下一lv, 如果未有得買即係未夠軍階<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣放炸彈<br />\nA. 1. 基礎戰先有得放<br />\n2. 去到基地搵 [ ! ]個ICON<br />\n3. 行到正確嘅位置,就會有話框叫你長按正方裝炸彈<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣出滾地 (緊急迴避)<br />\nA. 如果你部機有&rdquo;緊急迴避制御&ldquo; skill就可以連按兩次Boost掣使出急迴<br />\n(Default setting 即係連按X)<br />\n<br />\nQ:部機lv1用唔用到lv5武器？<br />\nA:無限場所有lv都得<br />\n限cost場要跟機lv, 高過部機過就降到你所持有嘅武器當中與機體同級或以下lv<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣出反格<br />\nA. 對方出格鬥時按三角撞埋去, 判定時機請自行練習<br />\n<br />\nQ. 格鬥點出二連斬三連斬<br />\nA. 機體要有&rdquo;格鬥連擊制御&ldquo; Skill, lv1可以2hit, lv2可以3hit<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解有人可以斬完又斬好似無硬直?<br />\nA. 運用Boost Cancel 技巧就可以解除攻擊後嘅硬直(包括火箭炮, 加農炮, 格鬥, etc), 方法係攻擊後立即輕按Boost step 走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手製SETTING建議<br />\n打之前改改手製個SETTING<br />\nDefault 用X加速搞到加速其間好難轉方向<br />\nR1轉武R2射又令人好易轉錯武<br />\n所以改成<br />\nR1射<br />\nR2轉武<br />\nL1加速<br />\nX跳<br />\n其他不變<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 浴缸裡的貓, One_For_All, 高熱火焰, 闇之大精靈,絕影OuO<br />\n<br />\n怎麼才算好泛機隊友? #曲<br />\n1.) 開場時散開衝, 唔好係我前面阻住我衝<br />\n2.) 到主戰場企係我前面擋彈, 等我定好位先好走<br />\n3.) 我射時唔該有後眼自動遠離我射線<br />\n4.) 我比人射時唔該有NT感應BOOST過黎幫我擋彈<br />\n5.) 擋完彈之後好馬上急回彈開等我可以零秒反擊<br />\n6.) 有格機打我你地要血肉長城保護我<br />\n7.) 就算因為保護我而死, 唔該死遠D免得爆炸D光影響我, D煙唔該飄遠D唔好影響我開鏡<br />\n<br />\n屌你班歐洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uKwdvWE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuKwdvWE.gif&h=34225e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tV2rxjL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtV2rxjL.gif&h=6a7dbb3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71a0c53a2bf0f5fd425121879439d5611f12c26f","tid":2301140,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"5粒鐘0回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050d51e17ed05233ee91b82faf2c17d07be19d3c","tid":2301140,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71a0c53a2bf0f5fd425121879439d5611f12c26f","tid":2301140,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"5粒鐘0回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T12:15:40.000Z","msg":"零的突破"},{"pid":"b51e8f5cef206b510add9e2e362498cafd999f3a","tid":2301140,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71a0c53a2bf0f5fd425121879439d5611f12c26f","tid":2301140,"uid":240342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"5粒鐘0回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T12:15:53.000Z","msg":"零的突破"}]}